   - FR-2.2: exception — afskrevet efter GIL § 16, stk. 1 → skalRetskraftvurderes = false (Test10)
   - FR-3.1 + FR-3.3: overskud + tvivlsom gæld → skalRetskraftvurdereOvskydende = true (Test11)
   - FR-3.1 via datafejl: overskud + datafejl-gæld → skalRetskraftvurdereOvskydende = true (Test12)
   - FR-3.1 negativ: ingen overskud → skalRetskraftvurdereOvskydende = false (Test13)
   - FR-3.1 negativ: overskud men ingen tvivlsom/datafejl-gæld → false (Test14)
   - FR-4.1 + FR-4.2: modregning + retskraftig gæld + overskud → daekRetskraftigForst = true (Test15)
   - FR-4.1 negativ: ikke modregningssituation → daekRetskraftigForst = false (Test16)

   Boundary dates used:
   - |2024-12-31|: GIL § 18c cutoff date (last eligible day, inclusive)
   - |2025-01-01|: first day AFTER cutoff (not eligible)
   - |2020-06-01|: historical date (well within eligible period)

   FR → Test mapping:
   FR-0.1  → Test01 (on cutoff), Test02 (after cutoff), Test03 (historical)
   FR-1.1  → Test04
   FR-1.2  → Test05
   FR-1.3  → Test06
   FR-1.4  → Test07 (datafejl flag)
   FR-2.1  → Test08 (positive), Test09 (negative)
   FR-2.2  → Test10 (exception)
   FR-3.1  → Test11 (tvivlsom), Test12 (datafejl), Test13 (ingen overskud), Test14 (ingen tvivlsom/datafejl)
   FR-3.3  → Test11, Test12 (skalRenterVurderesSidst = true)
   FR-4.1  → Test15 (positive), Test16 (negative)
